{"tid":315640,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"［新手］鏡頭問題","createTime":"2017-07-10T07:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T07:21:20.000Z","uid":122426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"264b7ed661032ad3b286c8682f8a28f2667e57b6","tid":315640,"uid":122426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"我想問下<br />\n我點樣先知道我部機用到邊啲鏡頭<br />\n例如：<br />\n我有一部Olympics OMD EM5 Mark II<br />\n我有無得用Nikon既鏡頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093bcbed26fd586d2c0ebe733339a0bfa41f17a6","tid":315640,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:19:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.google.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&d=HAPa5dXP9WoaLJ2U5vHgdcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=332dc1d9\" target=\"_blank\">www.google.com</a>"},{"pid":"f270f55a54447957dbaa71697371e948ffbe0088","tid":315640,"uid":114774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"睇下佢用咩mount"},{"pid":"53194d0dae3cd0d89b3ba3b8931b7b6d57231bd8","tid":315640,"uid":82629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:21:20.000Z","msg":"睇個接環 <br />\n通常枝鏡會寫係咩mount<br />\n例如枝鏡係比canon用既 會講明canon mount 咁其他就用唔到 <br />\n如果你想要果枝鏡無出你部機個mount 咁你可以買多個轉接環去用"}]}